name: Elements_hasTextTest
description: Unit tests for the hasText method of the Elements class.

test_cases.name: testHasTextWithText
test_cases.description: Tests the hasText method when the Elements object contains an Element with text.

test_cases.name: testHasTextWithoutText
test_cases.description: Tests the hasText method when the Elements object contains an Element without text.

test_cases.name: testHasTextMixed
test_cases.description: Tests the hasText method when the Elements object contains a mix of Elements with and without text.
